    "description": "Die Cutting VR是一款将日韩传统小游戏“脱模”改为赌博死亡游戏风格的VR游戏。<br><br><br>◆脱模<br>“脱模”可在VR模式下游玩，玩家须用针将点心抠成指定的形状。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/a81fb619e76dcb6c9e6867d47ba5c9ed.poster.avif?t=1638625948\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/a81fb619e76dcb6c9e6867d47ba5c9ed.webm?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/a81fb619e76dcb6c9e6867d47ba5c9ed.mp4?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>◆高额奖金（※游戏内记分）<br>抠得越漂亮、越多且形状越复杂，就能获得高额奖金。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/d0226e672927237a27a466e08b017b65.poster.avif?t=1638625948\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/d0226e672927237a27a466e08b017b65.webm?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/d0226e672927237a27a466e08b017b65.mp4?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>◆如果抠碎点心，游戏即刻结束<br>如果抠碎点心，游戏即刻结束。<br>如果在限定时间内没有抠出任何点心，游戏即刻结束。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/9609e8a3d5f926621fd0e2a8e8db6c4e.poster.avif?t=1638625948\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/9609e8a3d5f926621fd0e2a8e8db6c4e.webm?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/9609e8a3d5f926621fd0e2a8e8db6c4e.mp4?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>◆搭载最新的舔舔系统<br>搭载Chupa Chupa VR内曾采用过的创新游戏系统“舔舔系统”，为此允许玩家舔点心。<br>点心被舔过后就会溶化，然后即可轻松抠下。（※但需要时间）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/bb6856a14933d65642acb7780ca8edf3.poster.avif?t=1638625948\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/bb6856a14933d65642acb7780ca8edf3.webm?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794360/extras/bb6856a14933d65642acb7780ca8edf3.mp4?t=1638625948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>◆排名功能<br>附带排名功能，较量限定时间内所获得的奖金。",
